headline: T. ROWE PRICE GROUP REPORTS PRELIMINARY MONTH-END ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT FOR AUGUST 2025
summary: T. Rowe Price Group, Inc. (NASDAQ-GS: TROW) announced preliminary August month-end assets under management of $1.73 trillion. Preliminary net outflows for August 2025 were $5.9 billion.
